{"tid":1174252,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[烏克蘭]烏克蘭新總統Zelensky稱願意同不滿他的烏克蘭人溝通","createTime":"2019-05-27T16:47:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T19:42:22.000Z","uid":100986,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"60cd8125533c56786017577cf8cf2781c2e0fd23","tid":1174252,"uid":100986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T16:47:47.000Z","msg":"[烏克蘭]烏克蘭 烏克蘭新總統Zelensky稱不怕被批評 Zelensky願意同不滿他的烏克蘭選民溝通<br />\n***烏克蘭總統Zelensky被踢爆為烏克蘭+以色列富豪Ihor kolomoisky(烏克蘭同以色列雙重國籍以的代言人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img5.eadaily.com/r650x400/o/cdd/c692b9904b2235f0a89b4d82f8214.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg5.eadaily.com%2Fr650x400%2Fo%2Fcdd%2Fc692b9904b2235f0a89b4d82f8214.jpg&h=7c5e84f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn1.img.sputnik-news.ee/images//1559/25/15592529.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn1.img.sputnik-news.ee%2Fimages%2F%2F1559%2F25%2F15592529.jpg&h=4d0decfb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nZelensky on protesters demanding his impeachment: No measures needed if law obeyed<br />\n<br />\n26 May 2019<br />\n<br />\n16-year-old Darya Kotsyuruba and 20-year-old Roman Filiuk on Saturday, May 25, staged a rally in Rivne protesting against recent appointments by Zelensky. <br />\n<br />\nUkrainian President Volodymyr Zelensky has called on law-enforcement agencies not to take measures against political protesters if they obey law.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;I've figured out the situation regarding the alleged detention of a young man and a [teenage] girl who staged a protest against me in Rivne. There was no detention, but law enforcers could have acted softer. The police will conduct an official probe,&quot; Zelensky said on Facebook on Sunday, May 26.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;I call on the Interior Ministry not to take measures against political protesters if people obey law. I am not afraid of criticism,&quot; Zelensky said.<br />\n<br />\nEarlier, First Deputy Chairperson of the Verkhovna Rada Iryna Gerashchenko said she was drafting a request to the National Police regarding the detention of two young people in the city of Rivne who simultaneously staged one-person protests with posters insisting on the impeachment to the newly elected president.<br />\n<br />\n<strong>According to the local news outlet UA:Rivne, 16-year-old Darya Kotsyuruba and 20-year-old Roman Filiuk on Saturday, May 25, staged a rally in Rivne protesting against recent appointments by Zelensky. They held posters saying &quot;Ukraine beyond the law,&quot; &quot;President should be impeached,&quot; &quot;Acting as brothers rather than cronies,&quot; &quot;Said. Violated. Resigned.&quot;<br />\n<br />\nChief of Rivne city police department Vasyl Zelinsky said that the two had not been detained but invited to the police station for drawing up a protocol on administrative offences under Article 185-1 for the failure to inform authorities for holding a rally, protest event, and others. What is more, a protocol was issued against Darya Kotsyuruba's mother under Article 184 for bad parenting.</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.unian.net/photos/2019_05/1557792501-3055.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unian.net%2Fphotos%2F2019_05%2F1557792501-3055.jpg&h=b6f2d182&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.unian.info/society/10563690-zelensky-on-protesters-demanding-his-impeachment-no-measures-needed-if-law-obeyed.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.unian.info%2Fsociety%2F10563690-zelensky-on-protesters-demanding-his-impeachment-no-measures-needed-if-law-obeyed.html&d=4a077UaaKOqSfaiyS2iiQXvcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=79c53f60\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.unian.info/society/10563690-zelensky-on-protesters-demanding-his-impeachment-no-measures-needed-if-law-obeyed.html</a>"},{"pid":"c9a36120fdc23a6d3b621d4a25fb2688f4683246","tid":1174252,"uid":100986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T16:56:38.000Z","msg":"At the same time, the newly inaugurated president, a 41-year-old comedian and political neophyte, appointed Andriy Bohdan to head his presidential staff. He is the longtime lawyer of billionaire Ihor Kolomoisky, whose television channel has broadcast Mr. Zelensky&rsquo;s comedy shows for the last seven years. The attorney is barred from holding government-appointed positions until 2024 based on a lustration law that was passed in the wake of the Euro-Maidan Revolution. <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://news.liga.net/images/general/2019/04/26/thumbnail-tw-20190426130506-1464.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.liga.net%2Fimages%2Fgeneral%2F2019%2F04%2F26%2Fthumbnail-tw-20190426130506-1464.jpg&h=e2640221&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.ukrweekly.com/uwwp/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Page1_Ze-inauguration.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ukrweekly.com%2Fuwwp%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F05%2FPage1_Ze-inauguration.jpg&h=b6203d79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nZelensky inaugurated as Ukraine&rsquo;s sixth president<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.ukrweekly.com/uwwp/zelensky-inaugurated-as-ukraines-sixth-president/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ukrweekly.com%2Fuwwp%2Fzelensky-inaugurated-as-ukraines-sixth-president%2F&d=4a077UaaKOqSfaiyS2iiQXvcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=a61a2674\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ukrweekly.com/uwwp/zelensky-inaugurated-as-ukraines-sixth-president/</a>"},{"pid":"a35e17408b4afa0a8db2850c14f045a36b2a70bc","tid":1174252,"uid":100986,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T17:01:24.000Z","msg":"烏克蘭冇波蘭、愛沙尼亞、立陶宛同拉脫維亞咁好彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c32216f863a2acd781d262c563376d05599c2798","tid":1174252,"uid":41245,"like":2,"dislike":0